Project Ampule
Copyright 2026 Saltreach

This project is a spin-off of Project NOMAD, created by Crosstalk Solutions.
  https://github.com/Crosstalk-Solutions/project-nomad

Project NOMAD provided the original concept of an offline-first, local LLM
survival assistant. Project Ampule extends that idea with a RAG pipeline,
curated knowledge ingestion, and support for small ARM devices such as
Orange Pi and Raspberry Pi.
